        * Fixed update option for A Record
        * Adding fields for fixed address
        
        0.4.22 (2019-02-21)
        ___________________
        
        * Supported returning default fileds plus user required fields reflecting WAPI
        * Supporting 'aliases' parameter of HOST record for DNS
        
        0.4.21 (2019-01-18)
        ___________________
        
